Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_reg_queue_mode

Notes: Sets the number of queues and amount of local storage per queue The system has a total of 256 queues and (256*8) words of local command storage. This CSR sets the number of queues that are used. Increasing the value of MODE by 1 decreases the number of queues by a power of 2 and increases the local storage per queue by a power of 2. MODEn queues storage/queue 0 256 64B ( 8 words) 1 128 128B (16 words) 2 64 256B (32 words)
